title: a foreign library
pid: 70853a29-cf7d-4ad2-bf20-ffeca34dc8a6
body: |2-
  #+BEGIN_SRC haskell
  module Foreign where

  data Foo = Foo {..}

  bar :: Foo -> WhatBarReturns
    -- TODO: What about IO?
    --       What if the return value needs decoding?
  bar = ...

  baz :: Foo -> WhatBazReturns
  baz = ...
  #+END_SRC
